snippet.title: Puke - Official Teaser | English
snippet.description:
The teaser video of the video game Puke is now live!
The town of Puke is a place far from everything and hard to reach. The people of this town have been working in the same factory and eating from the same fields for generations. But this town's dirty secrets are waiting to be revealed.

Game Website: https://www.playpuke.com/
Company Website: https://www.skyfect.com/

Game Steam Page;
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2640130/Puke/

Don't forget to add it to your wish list!
You can use the links above for more information.
